My First Experience<br/>
<br/>
I had my first experience with this drug a few nights ago and while it was a good experience at its peak, the Comedown is not worth the experience for me. My body has been aching for 2 days and I can hardly move and it's the third day. I'm experiencing flu symptoms chest pain and I did a very very small amount. <br/>
<br/>
I did also drink alcohol during the experience so I think my body probably got very dehydrated even though I was drinking a lot of water. The high was nice because it was basically just a good feeling love and peace <div class="pullquote-right1"><div class="pullquote-text">it was basically just a good feeling love and peace</div></div>. But I didn't hallucinate or feel anything sexual or euphoric. Maybe had I done more, I would have felt something other than extreme amount of love and peace. I don't regret the experience but I will definitely never do it again because just with that tiny bit that I did my body is a wreck.<!-- End Body -->
<br/><br style="clear:both;"/>


